data.meta_description: 46 likes, 1 comments - bossming on June 24, 2024: "iO Italian Osteria is a highly rated Italian trattoria in HillV2 mall in upper bukit timah. I had bookmarked the find during one of my pandemic exploratory jaunts but did not get the chance to try it till today. It was a Monday night, but the space was bustling and packed! The food at iO transported me back to the time I had home cooked Italian food in Rome during a school trip. Every dish was executed well but with the heart and soul of a home cooked meal. Despite it being busy, the service also matched up, and the meal was reasonably priced (In today's day and age). A nice neighbourhood find!".
